*elemental table (see other doc)
*Deity of sorts for each element, influences neighboring environments
*coming of age pilgrimage to visit deity and obtain element
*anyone can get elements, only player and specials can combine
*each deity has different personalities quirks and challenges
*resolution and conscience are weak on their own and looked down on, but most powerful when combined with others
*can choose one starting element, something happens to the other two starting after you choose(?)
*player plays on “wrong side of the fence” most of the game
